tomer data platform<\/b><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When <a href=\"https:\/\/www.yclients.com\/blog\/en\/managing-your-service-business-online-all-in-one-solution-for-online-scheduling\/\">creating an appointment<\/a>, a client\u2019s name, contact information (phone and email), money spent, number, and dates of visits are added to the client base instantly. If necessary, you can edit it manually &#8212; for example, add actual or additional customers\u2019 phone numbers.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4291\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4291\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-4291 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/www.yclients.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/1-1024x625.png\" alt=\"client database customer data platform\" width=\"800\" height=\"488\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.yclients.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/1-1024x625.png 1024w, https:\/\/www.yclients.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/1-300x183.png 300w, https:\/\/www.yclients.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/1-768x469.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4291\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Client Database<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Make a discount system that benefits you<\/span><\/h2>\n<h4><b>Automatic discount calculation<\/b><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Set up the rules and client category &#8212; VIP, Loyal, Regular, or your custom one, and the discount for each client will be calculated automatically and displayed in the client base.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4292\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4292\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-large wp-image-4292\" src=\"https:\/\/www.yclients.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/2-1024x181.png\" alt=\"client management software client base\" width=\"800\