s by birthday, frequency of visits, booking status, and more. This will help you to apply customer relationship marketing by creating special offers and sending them to your clients. For instance, create a special offer for birthdays or your regular customers, or identify customers who have not come to you for a month and send them a special offer which they can\u2019t decline.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4294\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4294\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-4294 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/www.yclients.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/4-1024x412.png\" alt=\"customer segmentation client management software\" width=\"800\" height=\"322\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.yclients.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/4-1024x412.png 1024w, https:\/\/www.yclients.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/4-300x121.png 300w, https:\/\/www.yclients.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/4-768x309.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4294\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Customer segmentation with filters<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you need to find one specific client, the Client Database provides a quick search by name, phone, email, or loyalty card number.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Send newsletters and notifications in a few clicks<\/span><\/h2>\n<h4><b>Segment and select customers for automated text messages<\/b><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Upload data to Excel, add as many client categories as you need. Send an automated text message.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4295\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4295\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-4295 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/www.yclients.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/5-1024x283.png\" alt=\"client 